OL,3,CPride of Britain: Regional Fundraiser
OL,4,Cof the Year Finalist Lynne Blaney
OL,6,FIt is that time of year again where we
OL,7,Fcelebrate those from our communities
OL,8,Fwho have given their time to raise
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds to help others.
OL,11,FWe've been searching for the ITV
OL,12,FBorder Pride of Britain Regional
OL,13,FFundraiser of the Year, and have
OL,14,Fwhittled it down to four outstanding
OL,15,Ffinalists.
OL,17,FLynne Blaney, from Whitehaven, has
OL,18,Fraised more than #100,000 for cancer
OL,19,Fpatients at West Cumberland Hospital.
