OL,3,CPride of Britain: Regional Fundraiser
OL,4,Cof the Year Finalist Lynne Blaney
OL,6,FTen years ago, Lynne's husband Ged
OL,7,Fpassed away with cancer having been
OL,8,Ftreated at WCH's Henderson Suite.
OL,10,FWhile receiving chemotherapy, Ged had
OL,11,Fcreated a support group for patients
OL,12,Fat the Henderson Suite called Stronger
OL,13,FTogether, arranging walks, talks and
OL,14,Fafternoon tea for those in the ward.
OL,16,FFollowing his death, Lynne has spent
OL,17,Fthe decade fundraising to keep
OL,18,FStronger Together alive, buying care
OL,19,Fpackages for Henderson Suite patients
OL,20,Fto make their treatment easier.
