OL,3,CPride of Britain: Regional Fundraiser
OL,4,Cof the Year Finalist Lynne Blaney
OL,6,FLynne told us: "We donate things like
OL,7,Fblankets and drinks, anything to make
OL,8,Flife a little bit more comfortable. In
OL,9,Fchemotherapy, you get cold. So a
OL,10,Flittle blanket to wrap around you,
OL,11,Feven a puzzle book to take with you
OL,12,Ffor the day. Because it's a long day."
OL,14,FStronger Together helps to organise
OL,15,Fthe Ged Blaney & Arthur Lamb Memorial
OL,16,Fcricket match. Over the years, more
OL,17,Fthan #100,000 has been raised for the
OL,18,Fcancer patients in the Henderson Suite.
