OL,3,CPride of Britain: Regional Fundraiser
OL,4,Cof the Year Finalist Lynne Blaney
OL,6,FKerry Stewart, a cancer patient
OL,7,Freceiving treatment, said: "Yes. It
OL,8,Fjust makes a huge difference because
OL,9,Finstead of just going and sitting, you
OL,10,Fget a bit of luxury along with that,
OL,11,Fand it just makes the whole experience
OL,12,Fa bit better."
OL,14,FLynne has undertaken this fundraising
OL,15,Fwhile maintaining her full time job,
OL,16,Fregularly ringing NHS staff at the
OL,17,FHenderson Suite to find out what they
OL,18,For the patients need.
