OL,3,CPride of Britain: Regional Fundraiser
OL,4,Cof the Year Finalist Lynne Blaney
OL,6,FNicole Benson, deputy sister at the
OL,7,FHenderson Suite said: "She's just an
OL,8,Fincredible person. She does it on her
OL,9,Fown. She fetches and carries. She
OL,10,Fdoesn't ask for any help.
OL,12,F"She doesn't do it for the credit. She
OL,13,Fdoes it for the unit and for the
OL,14,Fpatients. And to me, that's just
OL,15,Famazing."
